#: .\ammo.json
msgid "fungicidal gas warhead .203"
msgid_plural "fungicidal gas warheads .203"
msgstr[0] "殺真菌氣體彈頭 .203"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fungicidal gas warhead .203', 'str_pl':
#. 'fungicidal gas warheads .203'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fungicidal gas warhead 7.62x51mm', 'str_pl':
#. 'fungicidal gas warheads 7.62x51mm'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fungicidal gas warhead .50 BMG', 'str_pl':
#. 'fungicidal gas warheads .50 BMG'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"It is a specially-made bullet that sprays the fungicidal gas sealed in the "
"warhead when it lands. There is almost no killing power and the amount of "
"glaze is modest to avoid warhead damage at launch."
msgstr "這是一種特製子彈，落地時會噴灑密封在彈頭內的殺真菌氣體。它幾乎沒有殺傷力，且釉料用量適中，以避免發射時彈頭受損。"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "fungicidal gas warhead 7.62x51mm"
msgid_plural "fungicidal gas warheads 7.62x51mm"
msgstr[0] "殺真菌氣體彈頭 7.62x51mm"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "fungicidal gas warhead .50 BMG"
msgid_plural "fungicidal gas warheads .50 BMG"
msgstr[0] "殺真菌氣體彈頭 .50 BMG"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "fungicide gas hand grenade"
msgid_plural "fungicide gas hand grenades"
msgstr[0] "殺真菌氣體手榴彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fungicide gas hand grenade', 'str_pl':
#. 'fungicide gas hand grenades'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"A hand grenade filled with fungicidal gas. Use to pull the pin and ignite. "
"It takes 5 turns to gas spout."
msgstr "一枚填充了殺真菌氣體的手榴彈。使用時需拉環並點燃。氣體噴發需要5回合。"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "fungicide gas hand grenade (active)"
msgid_plural "fungicide gas hand grenades (active)"
msgstr[0] "殺真菌氣體手榴彈（激活中）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fungicide gas hand grenade (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'fungicide gas hand grenades (active)'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"A hand grenade filled with fungicidal gas. The pin is already pulled and is "
"releasing gas."
msgstr "一枚填充了殺真菌氣體的手榴彈。拉環已拉開，正在釋放氣體。"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "40mm fungicidal gas grenade"
msgid_plural "40mm fungicidal gas grenades"
msgstr[0] "40毫米殺真菌氣體榴彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '40mm fungicidal gas grenade', 'str_pl': '40mm
#. fungicidal gas grenades'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"A 40 mm grenade bullet filled with fungicidal gas. For a while, we will keep"
" releasing the sterilizing gas to the impact point."
msgstr "一枚填充了殺真菌氣體的40毫米榴彈子彈。撞擊點將持續釋放消毒氣體一段時間。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "anti-fungal gear"
msgstr "抗真菌裝備"

#. ~ Description for anti-fungal gear
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "All fungus shall be destroyed."
msgstr "所有真菌都將被摧毀。"
